Kiele Sanchez https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kiele_Sanchez 0 Kiele Michelle Sanchez ( KEE-lee; born October 13, 1977) is an American actress who starred in the A Network drama The Glades. Previously, she had starred as Anne Sorelli in The WB comedy-drama Related and as Nikki Fernandez on the main cast in the third season of the ABC television drama series Lost. She also starred in the DirecTV drama series Kingdom on the Audience Network. Kiele_Michelle_Sanchez ( KEE-lee ; born October_13_,_1977 ) is an_American_actress who starred in the_A The_Glades .
